item.title: :o :o :o :o :o :o help!
item.dc:creator: @viruz_3 viruz 3
item.description:
@viruz_3 wrote:

0.0.0.0 means LocalHost and the npc you added … You added a Giant Rock Crab… In autospawn.cfg find the npc you added and do this:

spawn = 452(tab)Xcoord(tab)Ycoord(tab)0(tab)0(tab)0(tab)0(tab)2(tab) Giant Rock Crab

make sure you replace the “(tab)” with the tab button… Try that
